title: Frida Kahlo T-Shirt
description:
Frida Kahlo bravely shared her deepest feelings and struggles through her unique self-portraits. Her strength continues to inspire millions of people today. She captured the essence of her independence and openness when she wrote “I am my own muse.”
  • Material: Super soft and comfy Cotton, Polyester, Rayon blend
  • Tagless
  • Printed in Chicago
